title: Q: How can I style a tiddler if it has "this" OR "that" tag?
tags: [[Custom Styles FAQ]]

''Answer:'' <<.from-version "5.1.16">>

Either tag `this` or tag `that` create a red border.

```
[data-tags~="this"],
[data-tags~="that"] {
  border: 2px solid red;
}
```

